        "teachingPoint": "Focus your Block 2 input on the commercial and legal sections with the highest financial risk: pricing and payment terms, SLA and remedy provisions, liability and indemnification, termination rights, and any escalation or benchmarking mechanisms. If pasting a full contract, EXOS will process it — but if you have limited time, the liability, termination, and auto-renewal sections are always the highest priority for first-pass review.",
        "hook": "Auto-renewal clauses, uncapped liability, and missing SLA remedies hide in contracts until they cost you money. EXOS performs a first-pass contract risk analysis in minutes — flagging the top commercial risks and producing a prioritised redline brief so your legal team focuses on the clauses that matter, not the pages that don't.",
