        "hook": "Poorly specified RFPs produce bids that cannot be compared — forcing clarification rounds that extend procurement timelines by weeks and give suppliers room to hide cost. EXOS generates a fully structured, EU-compliant RFP in minutes. Industry benchmarks show well-structured tenders produce 12–18% more competitive pricing responses, simply because suppliers can price with confidence.",
