        "hook": "Supplier risk events don't announce themselves at quarterly reviews — by then, the early warning window has passed. EXOS monitors your supplier portfolio continuously, surfacing Δ-changes in risk scores and alerting your team when thresholds are breached. Catch financial distress, geopolitical exposure, and regulatory risk while you still have time to act.",
