        "hook": "Make vs. Buy decisions made without a structured framework reverse within 3 years at a cost of 2.5x the original investment. EXOS analyses the decision across financial, operational, strategic, and risk dimensions simultaneously — delivering a board-ready recommendation with sensitivity ranges in the time it takes to book a meeting.",
